input.sql:
select distinct
opp.id,
partner.CurrencyIsoCode,
cpm.id,
partner.PartnerTier,
partner.TransactionRole,

acct.id,
acct.Source_Record_Id__c,
CASE 
  WHEN acct.ID IS NOT NULL THEN acct.ID
  ELSE 
    CASE 
      WHEN partner.SuperRegion = 'NA' THEN '0016e00003Lc7wmAAB'
      WHEN partner.SuperRegion = 'EMEA' THEN '0016e00003X3hBlAAJ'
      WHEN partner.SuperRegion = 'LATAM' THEN '0016e00003Lc7xuAAB'
      WHEN partner.SuperRegion = 'APAC' THEN '0016e00003RWCSbAAP'
      ELSE '0016e00003Lc7wmAAB'
    END
END AS acct_Source_Record_Id__c

from  #{_dp('{"pill_type":"output","provider":"workato_smart_list","line":"f51a66d9","path":["list_name"]}')} as partner
left join #{_dp('{"pill_type":"output","provider":"workato_smart_list","line":"e8af18ef","path":["list_name"]}')} as opp
on partner.OppNumber = opp.OpportunityNumber__c

left join #{_dp('{"pill_type":"output","provider":"workato_smart_list","line":"b8681877","path":["list_name"]}')} as cp 
on partner.PartnerTypeName = cp.Name

left join #{_dp('{"pill_type":"output","provider":"workato_smart_list","line":"4b1c8aa2","path":["list_name"]}')} as acct on partner.AccountId
 = acct.source_record_id__c
 
 left join #{_dp('{"pill_type":"output","provider":"workato_smart_list","line":"479865ec","path":["list_name"]}')} as cpm on 
 acct.id = cpm.PartnerId and 
 cp.id = cpm.ProgramId
